<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5352850>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Live and preserved colouration of H. sesamum: A, MZB 17209, 36.7 mm SL, live male holotype; B, ZRC 54009, 47.0 mm SL, preserved male; C, MZB 17210, 44.4 mm SL, live female; D, ZRC 54009, 44.3 mm SL, preserved female (not to scale)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5352850/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5352852>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Dorsal fin and anal fin colouration of male H. sesamum: A, live holotype, MZB 17209, 36.7 mm SL; B, ZRC 54009, 47.0 mm SL (white background); C, ZRC 54009, 47.0 mm SL (black background)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5352852/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5352854>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Dorsal fin and anal fin colouration of female H. sesamum: A, live paratype, MZB 17210 (with damaged dorsal and caudal fins), 44.4 mm SL; B, ZRC 54009, 44.3 mm SL." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5352854/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5352856>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Dorsal fin morphology of freshly preserved H. sesamum male, ZRC 54009, 47.0 mm SL." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5352856/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5352860>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Lower jaw colouration of H. sesamum: A, MZB 17209, 36.7 mm SL, live male holotype; B, ZRC 54009, 47.0 mm SL, preserved male; C, MZB 17210, 44.4 mm SL, live female; D, ZRC 54009, 44.3 mm SL, preserved female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5352860/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5352858>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Radiographs of anal fin of H. sesamum: A, MZB 17209, holotype, 36.7 mm SL male; B, MZB 17210, paratype, 44.4 mm SL female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5352858/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5352862>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Distribution of H. sesamum (solid circle), H. byssus (solid square) and H. kecil (hollow circle) in Borneo." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5352862/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5352864>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Habitat of H. sesamum, South Kalimantan: Batulicin basin (2011)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5352864/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

